│ 13580 /// Merges shuffle masks and emits final shuffle instruction, if required. It                                                                                                                            │
│ 13581 /// supports shuffling of 2 input vectors. It implements lazy shuffles emission,                                                                                                                         │
│ 13582 /// when the actual shuffle instruction is generated only if this is actually                                                                                                                            │
│ 13583 /// required. Otherwise, the shuffle instruction emission is delayed till the                                                                                                                            │
│ 13584 /// end of the process, to reduce the number of emitted instructions and further                                                                                                                         │
│ 13585 /// analysis/transformations.                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ 13586 /// The class also will look through the previously emitted shuffle instructions                                                                                                                         │
│ 13587 /// and properly mark indices in mask as undef.                                                                                                                                                          │
│ 13588 /// For example, given the code                                                                                                                                                                          │
